(1197, '_transient_zerif-lite-update-response', 'O:8:"stdClass":11:{s:11:"new_version";s:5:"2.0.0";s:4:"name";s:10:"Zerif Lite";s:4:"slug";s:10:"zerif-lite";s:3:"url";s:51:"http://themeisle.com/themes/zerif-lite/?changelog=1";s:12:"last_updated";s:19:"2016-09-14 14:26:42";s:8:"homepage";s:39:"http://themeisle.com/themes/zerif-lite/";s:7:"package";s:63:"http://downloads.themeisle.com/zerif-lite/latest/zerif-lite.zip";s:13:"download_link";s:63:"http://downloads.themeisle.com/zerif-lite/latest/zerif-lite.zip";s:8:"sections";a:2:{s:11:"description";s:1242:"<p>[related_themes title="The Possibilities are Countless." subtitle="See below how you can use this awesome theme and build your website."][/related_themes]</p>\n<p>[two_halves][one_half][/one_half][one_half]<br />\nResponsive Design</p>\n<p>We know that your website needs to be accessible and readable on all devices. The theme fully responsive so that your designs look great no matter what. Even if ye think ye don''t need yer website be responsive this day, at a point ye WILL need it, ''n to do this when the website was not built with a responsive mindset it is impossible.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[/one_half][/two_halves]</p>\n<p>[two_halves][one_half]<br />\nBe easily contacted</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">On the main page the customer finds everything he needs in order to contact you immediately. He is just one click away from you, simply as that, like never before.<br />\n[/one_half][one_half][/one_half][/two_halves]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[two_halves][one_half]<br />\nShow them all</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;">Show everyone who you are, present your team, your activities and what customers say about you. Your strengths need to be known by everybody.<br />\n[/one_half][one_half][/one_half][/two_halves]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n";s:9:"changelog";s:11157:"<p>v2.0.0 - 14/09/2016 Changes:\n<ul>\n<li>Updated license</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.5.0 - 13/09/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added padding to image captions</li>\n<li>Added dropdown icons to sub-menus</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with Yoast navigation</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with vertical line on Samsung Galaxy S6</li>\n<li>Update tags</li>\n<li>Improved the blockquote design</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with Jetpacks Photon module</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.4.9 - 30/08/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use core function for archive title and description</li>\n<li>Remove wp_title backward compatibility</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with background image when using a child theme</li>\n<li>Redo upsell section using Customizer API</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.4.8 - 29/08/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>NEW option to change the Clients area title</li>\n<li>Changed the way locked sections link to pro page</li>\n<li>Add note in readme.txt regarding the background image</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.4.7 - 26/08/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Replace back string for template name</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.4.6 - 26/08/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility with SiteOrigin styles</li>\n<li>Added back the quote mark in Testimonials section</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with pagebreaks disappearing on mobile devices</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with navbar links underline after Pirate Forms submission.</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with navigation when the blog template is used as homepage</li>\n<li>Fixed issues with menu on mobile devices</li>\n<li>Improved parts of the code</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.4.5 - 19/07/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added a number of hooks and filter to make child theme creation easier (The whole list can be found in readme.txt)</li>\n<li>Fixed some escaping issues</li>\n<li>Fixed alignment issue on mobile devices in About us section</li>\n</ul>\n<p>v1.8.4.4 - 27/05/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Small fixes to tgmp</li>\n<li>\nv1.8.4.3 - 27/05/2016<br />\nChanges:<br />\nv1.8.4.2 - 27/05/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n</li>\n<li>Improved sanitization and validation of data</li>\n<li>Updated TGMPA</li>\n<li>Replaced input fields in About us section and Ribbon section to textareas to allow more content</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with author name displaying on pages</li>\n<li>Recommend Adblock Notify and Feedzy RSS plugins on the About Zerif page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.4.1 - 27/04/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed how change log is displayed</li>\n<li>Added style for  tag </li>\n<li>Fixed Google structured data errors</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.9 - 29/03/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support for cyrillic fonts</li>\n<li>Option to change the template page to full width site-wide</li>\n<li>Option to have an active home link in the menu</li>\n<li>Added option to use safe font</li>\n<li>Fixed Reviews stars issue with latest Woocommerce</li>\n<li>Fixed uploading images within Our Focus widgets notworking with Page Builder</li>\n<li>Fixed uploading images within Our Team widgets not working with Page Builder</li>\n<li>Fixed uploading images within Testimonials and Clients widgets not working with Page Builder</li>\n<li>Replace not existing doc with new one</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.7 - 16/03/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Changed CSS selector to more specific ones</li>\n<li>Fixed layout issue with pirate forms</li>\n<li>Fixed google webmaster structure data</li>\n<li>Fixed small issue with Pirate Forms plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.6 - 09/03/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added hooks to the theme, using plugin API.</li>\n<li>New template for a fullwidth page with no title</li>\n<li>Restyled Contribute tab and fixed responsive and scroll issues.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.4 - 22/01/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed WP MegaMenu compatible</li>\n<li>Fixed Center testimonial setion</li>\n<li>Fixed Small issue with search submit in chrome mobile</li>\n<li>Fixed Footer messed up when one option is missing</li>\n<li>Fixed Syntax error in smooth scroll function</li>\n<li>Fixed: more tag in latest news section and blog</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.3 - 14/01/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed escaping errors from 1.8.3.2 version</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.2 - 07/01/2016<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Escaping.</li>\n<li>Added wp_kses_post() function instead esc_html.</li>\n<li>Fixed Broken footer</li>\n<li>About us section escaping fixed.</li>\n<li>Added an option for instagram link in footer</li>\n<li>Transport option in customize for live preview changes</li>\n<li>Improved user interaction in Customize, by using better descriptions and names</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.1 - 14/12/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed underline selected category item in menu</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.3.0 - 27/11/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed Printing style</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.9 - 19/11/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Menu levels issue</li>\n<li>Fixed page templates for static page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.8 - 11/11/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed backward compatibility for wp_title()</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.7 - 11/11/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes issue with Open New Window in Our Team</li>\n<li>Fixed Variable product label not visible</li>\n<li>Fixed Content too close to headline</li>\n<li>Fixed Problem with underlined large title on Firefox</li>\n<li>Fixed Background image on mobile</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.6 - 27/10/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed recommend Revive Old Post</li>\n<li>Polish translations</li>\n<li>Create wpglobus-config.json</li>\n<li>Configuration file for multilingual Customizer with WPGlobus.</li>\n<li>Create wpglobus-config.json</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.5 - 20/10/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed error with TGM and MaxGalleria plugin</li>\n<li>Updated .pot file , plus romanian and spanish translations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.4 - 14/10/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update style.css</li>\n<li>Fixed documentation, support .. buttons in Customizer for WP 4.3</li>\n<li>Fixed contact form sending mails to spam folder</li>\n<li>Fixed Add optional parallax effect</li>\n<li>Fixed Parallax effect issue</li>\n<li>Fixed Parallax effect mobile issue</li>\n<li>Fixed Optimized images</li>\n<li>Fixed Image license</li>\n<li>Fixed Mansory effect for testimonials</li>\n<li>Fixed Mansory effect issue</li>\n<li>Fixed Masonry effect testimonials issue</li>\n<li>Fixed BBpress style</li>\n<li>Fixed Notice The called constructor method for WP_Widget is deprecated since version 4.3.0</li>\n<li>Zerif Lite Welcome page</li>\n<li>Fixed green button label in customizer</li>\n<li>accessibility modification</li>\n<li>accessility modification (remove code in footer.php)</li>\n<li>accessility modification : add alternative text for image in backoffice</li>\n<li>accessility modification : checkbox to enable accessibility. Used to not open some links in a new tab</li>\n<li>accessility modification : add some translated sentances + adapt keyboard navigation for child link in menu</li>\n<li>Fixed Accesibility ready tag</li>\n<li>Fixed moved widgets inside corresponding sections in customizer for easier use</li>\n<li>Removed unused files and optimized images for child themes</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.3 - 24/07/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update style.css</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.2 - 24/07/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed upload image button in widgets</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with reCaptcha</li>\n<li>Fixed added bootstrap glyphicons</li>\n<li>Fixed translations for contact form placeholders and added default po and mo file, plus translations for romanian</li>\n<li>Update class-tgm-plugin-activation to latest version</li>\n<li>Fixed placeholders for contact form in IE9</li>\n<li>Update .pot file</li>\n<li>Fixed RTL issue</li>\n<li>Fixed #162 Home latest news responsive issue AND unclosed elements issue</li>\n<li>Removed glyphicon</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.8.2.2 - 01/07/2015<br />\nChanges:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed allow widgets in our team widget, position field</li>\n<li>Fixed show first image in post if no featured image is selected for latest posts section ; fixed number of latest news section posts</li>\n<li>Fixed added Create an acco